Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台機動戰士是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是UE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在保護城市啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鬧扎拉姆的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子不小啊 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為UE出現才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE 外星人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你這個大戰外星人的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是何方來客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大搖大擺開著機動戰士出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我手下的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如你所見 年紀尚小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也常為他傷透了腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古…古魯迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼古魯迪克先生會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他們憑什麼抓走菲利特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條街是扎拉姆的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著外來者不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被敵對的艾烏巴瞧不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地盤之爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的聯邦軍是幹什麼吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴之間的摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍一向視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這裏的潛規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和菲利特有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 把拖車開過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去要回菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開軍用車去就鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了 我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在同一座衛星裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻動用機動戰士打仗的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺不擔心菲利特的安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座衛星太奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找回菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拖車著實不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我的卡車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就停在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定比跑著去要快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊瓦克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 坐下吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是衛星上少見的天然食材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯過這村就沒這店了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身份不是明確了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛逮住就馬上放人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被艾烏巴的人瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有空在乎那些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE不知什麼時候又會來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真到那時候再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說下次遇襲的可能是艾烏巴的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭不是早就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必沒完沒了 至今還這麼敵視？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們還自稱艾烏巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就必須為扎拉姆而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 完全無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們祖祖輩輩為扎拉姆而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這更崇高和有尊嚴的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 那台叫高達的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓給我如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們扎拉姆引以為豪的高性能機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gila一擁而上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也費了好大的功夫才制服它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼大的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能輕易干翻艾烏巴的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用高達…做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 加上高達的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦的事可以細談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們提供的條件已經足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在戰艦之外另加金額
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達不會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用高達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承死去母親的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯扎先生的遺志！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因UE失去雙親的孩子和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去妻兒的艦長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說我們糾纏於過去的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也是和過去糾纏不清的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看他那樣 小傢伙可精明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在享受大餐也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也討厭整天打架的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這不是莉莉亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 正準備去和扎拉姆講理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 也帶上我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對扎拉姆和艾烏巴有得是話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莉莉亞 有好玩的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 帶上他們好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼好不好 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和軟禁有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了UE的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為摧毀它 需要戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的巢穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的根據地？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀那裏的話 這場戰爭就會結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼非要從這裏買戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告聯邦軍總司令部的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更大的艦隊也不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是UE 豈能指望如今的聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍如果真有作戰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉也不會被毀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙親也不至會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去妻兒的艦長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生被UE奪走了家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的機師是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而能夠對它進行最佳指揮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特沒有任何錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即放了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法丁不是扎拉姆和艾烏巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少拽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我爸爸道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許欺負我的好爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有莉莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一車孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何處置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Gila出去嚇跑他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒空陪孩子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 孩子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾烏巴那群雜種…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的勝負還沒分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勒克特·艾法梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為高貴的艾烏巴騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛愛機Elmeda前來拜訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面專程前來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓客人空手回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫的機動戰士Gala呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 隨時可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院裏的機動戰士怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧不上那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾烏巴的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒克特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 這裏危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 快上車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏離城區遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上孩子們先回天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子 和扎拉姆艾烏巴根本無關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gila不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高貴的Elmeda面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有一敗塗地啊 扎拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以扎拉姆之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不會諂媚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾烏巴的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為昨天做個了結是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冬波老爹 親自做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 老年人請自重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以高貴的艾烏巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以艾烏巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆是宇宙最強！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了搞偷襲一無是處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 讓你囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 為什麼要打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的戰爭也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天打架今天還惦記著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不男人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為進行著這樣的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會連累無辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是為以前的事打打殺殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那台高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想否認！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把菲利特跟你們混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個外人知道什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些讓人們不幸的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆和艾烏巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是在一個衛星上生活的夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的機動戰士型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台離開編隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 古魯迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台衝我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是古魯迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在郊外發現一台UE機動戰士型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中的Genoace立即出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這裏也需要高達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼 別礙事 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 輪不到小孩出場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是砸我們地盤的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論艾烏巴還是UE都一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們扎拉姆自己對付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老大說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE之類艾烏巴足以應付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下它們的首級揚名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以艾烏巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆 艾烏巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆 艾烏巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要堅持到艾米莉她們逃進宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了 是宇宙港的升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 活著嗎 回話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特回天神號上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說AGE系統造出了了不得的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以對抗那台機動戰士的新式武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯已經在準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Genoace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍機師的骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星內部情況如何
